name: Elizabeth Soriano Tendero
text: MacGyver, nakakatatak na sa brain ko forever. Also, I personally like GoT, Six Feet Under,  Amazing Stories (John Williams!).     I hate yung kanta sa OITNB, show is ok but I skip through the OBB.
